'''天主教佩爾普林教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Pelplinensis}}；{{lang-pl|Diecezja pelplińska}}）是[[波蘭|波蘭]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]。教座位於[[佩爾普林|佩爾普林]]。屬[[天主教格但斯克總教區|格但斯克總教區]]。

始於1243年7月29日，稱為'''庫爾姆教區'''，1992年3月25日易名至今。<ref name="">{{cite journal|journal=[[宗座公報|宗座公報]]|publisher=梵蒂岡出版社|volume=84|title=''Totus Tuus Poloniae populus''|page=1099|url=http://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS%2084%20%5B1992%5D%20-%20ocr.pdf|access-date=2012-07-16|archive-date=2020-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200713051903/http://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS%2084%20%5B1992%5D%20-%20ocr.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2011年，在當地781,600人口中，有教友731,800人，佔轄區總人口93.6%、290個堂區、561名司鐸、1名執事、66名修士、102名修女。現任主教為{{link-pl|利則·卡瑟納|Ryszard Kasyna}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 27.10.2012 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2012/10/27/0613/01397.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-04-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190405152252/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2012/10/27/0613/01397.html |archivedate=2019-04-05 |language=it |date=2012-10-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-pl|阿爾卡迪烏什·奧克羅伊|Arkadiusz Okroj}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 12.02.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/02/12/190212b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-07-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190717062159/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/02/12/190212b.html |archivedate=2019-07-17 |language=en |date=2019-02-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休輔理主教為{{link-pl|伯多祿·克魯帕 (主教)|Piotr Krupa (biskup)|伯多祿·克魯帕}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 15.09.2011 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2011/09/15/0534/01278.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-04-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190405160030/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2011/09/15/0534/01278.html |archivedate=2019-04-05 |language=it |date=2011-09-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

